</sp><L>He said, and climb'd a stranded lighter's height, 
<L>Shot to the black abyss, and plung'd downright. 
<L>The Senior's judgment all the crowd admire, 
<L>Who but to sink the deeper, rose the higher. 
<L>Next Smedley div'd; low circles dimpled o&lsquo;er <pb id="P.421" n="421"> 
